{"title":"GPT-SoVITS","uid":"4b4ad76e40a6aec8ebb922b2fb9d3aaa","slug":"opensource/music/GPT-SoVITS","date":"2024-03-17T14:44:58.726Z","updated":"2024-03-16T11:44:51.905Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/opensource/music/GPT-SoVITS.json","keywords":"AIGC,LLM,糖果AIGC实验室","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"gpt-sovits\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#gpt-sovits\"></a> GPT-SoVITS</h1>\n<p>在 GitHub 上刚开源的一款适用于中文语音克隆的工具：GPT-SoVITS。</p>\n<p>仅需提供 5 秒语音样本，1 分钟完成声音克隆并训练出高质量的 TTS 模型！</p>\n<p>GitHub：<a href=\"http://github.com/RVC-Boss/GPT-SoVITS\">github.com/RVC-Boss/GPT-SoVITS</a></p>\n<p>目前已获得 1.1k Star，看到很多人对其评价为目前最强中文语音克隆工具。</p>\n<p>特征：<br />\n★ 零样本 TTS：输入 5 秒语音样本并体验即时文本到语音转换。</p>\n<p>★ Few-shot TTS：仅用 1 分钟的训练数据即可微调模型，以提高语音相似度和真实感。</p>\n<p>★ 跨语言支持：用与训练数据集不同的语言进行推理，目前支持英语、日语和中文。</p>\n<p>★ WebUI工具：集成工具包括语音伴奏分离、自动训练集分割、中文ASR和文本标注，帮助初学者创建训练数据集和GPT/SoVITS模型。</p>\n","text":" GPT-SoVITS 在 GitHub 上刚开源的一款适用于中文语音克隆的工具：GPT-SoVITS。 仅需提供 5 秒语音样本，1 分钟完成声音克隆并训练出高质量的 TTS 模型！ GitHub：github.com/RVC-Boss/GPT-SoVITS 目前已获得 1.1...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":365,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"github","slug":"github","count":1,"path":"api/categories/github.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"github","slug":"github","count":6,"path":"api/tags/github.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#gpt-sovits\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> GPT-SoVITS</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"安全书","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"《墨守之道-Web服务安全架构与实践》","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/shengnoah","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/3732639263","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/openresty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Meta开源了AI 音频生成工具 AudioCraft","uid":"868e3cd853e2fb25fbbd3b9fcb1e1038","slug":"opensource/music/Meta开源了AI 音频生成工具 AudioCraft","date":"202